             was indicted for <rs id="t18000219-83-off502" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000219-83-off502" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-83-off502" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000219-83-cd503" type="crimeDate">20th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-83-off502 t18000219-83-cd503"></join>, a silk cloak, value 2l. 10s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000219-83-victim764" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Waithman
                  <interp inst="t18000219-83-victim764" type="surname" value="Waithman"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-83-victim764" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
