                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-83-defend762 t18000219-83-punish506"></join>
               Confined one month in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18000219-83-punish507" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000219-83-punish507" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-83-punish507" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="privateWhipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-83-defend762 t18000219-83-punish507"></join>
               privately whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
